Advanced database knowledge in terms of optimisation and complex querying is highly favourable.
Working knowledge of using internal and external APIs in various formats including JSON and XML
Foundational knowledge of SQL databases with preference to experience working with MariaDB.
Experience working with Git version control.

Working concessions
Whilst the usual work time is during normal business hours Monday through Friday, responsibilities sometimes require working evenings and weekends to meet timelines agreed with the customers at times with little advance notice.

