We’re looking for a highly technical engineer to build and scale our on-chain trading infrastructure. You’ll turn trading and research ideas into robust, automated systems and work closely with traders and researchers to deploy capital efficiently across CEX and DeFi. Fluency in Chinese and English is required for daily collaboration.

